<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ru"><head>
<meta charset="utf-8"/>
<meta content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" name="viewport"/>
<title>New Chat Confirmation Light - Refined</title>
<script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com?plugins=forms,typography,container-queries"></script>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" rel="preconnect"/>
<link crossorigin="" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" rel="preconnect"/>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700&amp;display=swap" rel="stylesheet"/>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Material+Symbols+Outlined:wght,FILL@100..700,0..1&amp;display=swap" rel="stylesheet"/>
<script>
        tailwind.config = {
            theme: {
                extend: {
                    colors: {
                        primary: "#F85149",
                        "coral-red": "#FF5A5F",
                        "soft-grey": "#8E8E93",
                    },
                    fontFamily: {
                        sans: ['Inter', 'sans-serif'],
                    },
                    boxShadow: {
                        'liquid-glass': '0 8px 32px 0 rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08)',
                        'button-glow': '0 10px 20px rgba(255, 90, 95, 0.3)',
                        'inner-shine': 'inset 0 1px 1px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.4)',
                        'sheet-top': '0 -10px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.05)',
                    },
                    backdropBlur: {
                        'xs': '2px',
                        'xl': '24px',
                        'heavy': '40px',
                    },
                },
            },
        };
    </script>
<style type="text/tailwindcss">
        @layer utilities {
            .liquid-glass-sheet {
                @apply bg-white/70 backdrop-blur-heavy border-t border-white/60 shadow-sheet-top rounded-t-[2.5rem];
            }
            .liquid-glass-button-primary {
                @apply bg-coral-red text-white shadow-button-glow border-t border-white/30 relative overflow-hidden;
                background: linear-gradient(180deg, #FF6B6F 0%, #FF5A5F 100%);
            }
            .liquid-glass-button-secondary {
                @apply bg-black/5 hover:bg-black/10 text-slate-600 backdrop-blur-md transition-all border border-white/40;
            }
            .shine-overlay {
                background: linear-gradient(
                    to bottom,
                    rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.4) 0%,
                    rgba(255, 255, 255, 0) 60%
                );
            }
            .liquid-circle-red {
                background: linear-gradient(135deg, #FF6B6F 0%, #F85149 100%);
                @apply shadow-[0_12px_24px_rgba(248,81,73,0.35),inset_0_1px_2px_rgba(255,255,255,0.4)];
            }
        }
    </style>
<style>
        body {
            min-height: 100dvh;
            min-height: max(884px, 100dvh);
        }
    </style>
<style>
    body {
      min-height: max(884px, 100dvh);
    }
  </style>
  </head>
<body class="bg-[#f2f2f7] min-h-screen flex flex-col font-sans antialiased relative overflow-hidden">
<div class="absolute inset-0 z-0">
<div class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-full h-full bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-100/50 via-white to-purple-100/50 opacity-100"></div>
<div class="absolute top-1/4 left-1/4 w-96 h-96 bg-blue-400 rounded-full mix-blend-multiply filter blur-[120px] opacity-20"></div>
<div class="absolute bottom-1/4 right-1/4 w-96 h-96 bg-coral-red rounded-full mix-blend-multiply filter blur-[120px] opacity-10"></div>
<div class="w-full h-full flex flex-col p-6 opacity-30 blur-[4px] pointer-events-none select-none">
<div class="h-16 w-full bg-white rounded-2xl mb-6 shadow-sm"></div>
<div class="flex gap-4 mb-6">
<div class="h-32 w-full bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-sm"></div>
</div>
<div class="h-64 w-full bg-white rounded-2xl mb-6 shadow-sm"></div>
<div class="h-20 w-full bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-sm"></div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="fixed inset-0 bg-black/5 backdrop-blur-[12px] z-20"></div>
<div class="fixed inset-x-0 bottom-0 z-30 flex items-end justify-center w-full">
<div class="liquid-glass-sheet w-full max-w-lg mx-auto pb-12 pt-4 px-6 flex flex-col items-center relative transform transition-transform duration-500 translate-y-0">
<div class="w-10 h-1.5 bg-black/10 rounded-full mb-8 mx-auto"></div>
<div class="flex flex-col items-center text-center w-full max-w-sm mx-auto">
<div class="relative w-20 h-20 mb-6 flex items-center justify-center">
<div class="absolute inset-0 bg-coral-red/30 rounded-full blur-2xl opacity-60"></div>
<div class="relative w-16 h-16 liquid-circle-red rounded-full flex items-center justify-center border border-white/30">
<div class="relative w-9 h-9 flex items-center justify-center">
<svg class="w-full h-full text-white fill-current" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
<path d="M20 2H4C2.9 2 2 2.9 2 4V22L6 18H20C21.1 18 22 17.1 22 16V4C22 2.9 21.1 2 20 2Z"></path>
</svg>
<div class="absolute inset-0 flex items-center justify-center pb-1">
<svg class="w-4 h-4 text-coral-red fill-none stroke-[4] stroke-current" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
<path d="M12 5V19M5 12H19" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"></path>
</svg>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2 tracking-tight">
                    Начать новый чат?
                </h2>
<p class="text-[16px] text-soft-grey mb-10 leading-snug font-normal px-6">
                    Текущая история чата будет сохранена в истории диалогов
                </p>
<div class="w-full space-y-3">
<button class="w-full h-14 rounded-2xl liquid-glass-button-primary font-bold text-[17px] tracking-wide active:scale-[0.98] transition-transform flex items-center justify-center">
<span class="shine-overlay absolute inset-0 pointer-events-none"></span>
<span class="relative z-10">Начать</span>
</button>
<button class="w-full h-14 rounded-2xl liquid-glass-button-secondary font-semibold text-[17px] tracking-wide active:opacity-70 transition-opacity">
                        Отмена
                    </button>
</div>
</div>
<div class="h-6 w-full"></div>
</div>
</div>

</body></html>